[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02790\" class=\"\">Listen</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me <st data-num=\"02790\" class=\"\">in silence</st>, you <st data-num=\"0339\" class=\"\">coastlands</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Let the <st data-num=\"03816\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"02498\" class=\"\">find renewed</st> <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">strength</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Let them <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">approach</st> and <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">then</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">speak</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">let us <st data-num=\"07126\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st> for <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">debate</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">stirs up</st> this one from the <st data-num=\"04217\" class=\"\">east</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Who<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06664\" class=\"\">officially</st> <st data-num=\"07121\">commissions</st> him for <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">service</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">hands</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">over to</st> him<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and enables him to <st data-num=\"07287\" class=\"\">subdue</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">kings</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">makes</st> them like <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">dust</st> with his <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"05086\" class=\"\">windblown</st> <st data-num=\"07179\" class=\"\">straw</st> with his <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bow</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">pursues</st> them and <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passes by</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">unharmed</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">advances</st> <st data-num=\"0734 07272 03808\">with great speed</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"06466\" class=\"\">acts</st> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">carries out</st> decrees?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Who<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summons</st> the successive <st data-num=\"01755\" class=\"\">generations</st> from the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">beginning</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, am present <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">at the very beginning</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"0314\" class=\"\">the very end</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">one</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0339\" class=\"\">coastlands</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> and <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">are afraid</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"07098\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02729\" class=\"\">trembles</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"07126\" class=\"\">approach</st> and <st data-num=\"0857\" class=\"\">come</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">help</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">another</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">one <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> to the <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">other</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">Be strong</st>!\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02796\" class=\"\">craftsman</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">encourages</st> the <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">metalsmith</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the one who <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">wields</st> the <st data-num=\"06360\" class=\"\">hammer</st> encourages<n id=\"1\" /> the one who <st data-num=\"01986\" class=\"\">pounds</st> on the <st data-num=\"06471\">anvil</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">approves</st> the <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">quality</st> of the <st data-num=\"01694\" class=\"\">welding</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"04548\" class=\"\">nails</st> it <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">down</st> so it <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">won\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"04131\" class=\"\">fall over</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st>, my <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>, <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I have <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">offspring</st> of <st data-num=\"085\" class=\"\">Abraham</st> my <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">friend</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I am <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">bringing back</st><n id=\"1\" /> from the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07098\" class=\"\">extremities</st><p class=\"poetry\">and have <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st> from the <st data-num=\"0678\" class=\"\">remote regions</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> you, \u2018<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> are my <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>.\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st> you and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> you.</p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> be frightened, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0553\" class=\"\">strengthen</st> you\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">yes</st>, I <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">help</st> you\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">yes</st>, I <st data-num=\"08551\" class=\"\">uphold</st> you with my <st data-num=\"06664\" class=\"\">victorious</st> <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right hand</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">were angry</st> at you will <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">be ashamed</st> and <st data-num=\"03637\" class=\"\">humiliated</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"0376 07379\">adversaries</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> reduced to <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nothing</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">perish</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When you will <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">look for</st> your <st data-num=\"0376 04695\">opponents</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> you will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">find</st> them;<p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"0376 04421\">enemies</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> reduced to <st data-num=\"0657\" class=\"\">absolutely</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nothing</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the one who <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">takes hold of</st> your <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right hand</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> to you, \u2018<st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">helping</st> you.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>, <st data-num=\"08438\" class=\"\">despised, insignificant</st> <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04962\" class=\"\">men</st> of<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">helping</st> you,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">Protector</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, I am <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">making</st> you like<n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"02742\" class=\"\">sharp</st> <st data-num=\"04173\" class=\"\">threshing sledge</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02319\" class=\"\">new</st> and <st data-num=\"01167 06374\">double-edged</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You will <st data-num=\"01758\" class=\"\">thresh</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> and <st data-num=\"01854\" class=\"\">crush</st> them;<p class=\"poetry\">you will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st> like <st data-num=\"04671\" class=\"\">straw</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You will <st data-num=\"02219\" class=\"\">winnow</st> them and the <st data-num=\"07307\">wind</st> will <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">blow</st> them <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">away</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05591\">wind</st> will <st data-num=\"06327\" class=\"\">scatter</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> will <st data-num=\"01523\" class=\"\">rejoice</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>;<p class=\"poetry\">you will <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st> in the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06041\" class=\"\">oppressed</st> and the <st data-num=\"034\" class=\"\">poor</st> <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">look for</st> <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st>, but <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is none</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">tongues</st> <st data-num=\"05405\" class=\"\">are parched</st> from <st data-num=\"06772\" class=\"\">thirst</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, will <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">respond</st> to their prayers;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandon</st> them.</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">streams</st> <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">flow</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">down</st> the <st data-num=\"08205\" class=\"\">slopes</st><p class=\"poetry\">and produce <st data-num=\"04599\" class=\"\">springs</st> in the <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">middle</st> of the <st data-num=\"01237\" class=\"\">valleys</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">turn</st> the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st> into a <st data-num=\"098\" class=\"\">pool</st> of <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st><p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"06723\" class=\"\">arid</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> into <st data-num=\"04161 04325\">springs</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"0730\" class=\"\">cedars</st>, <st data-num=\"07848\" class=\"\">acacias</st>, <st data-num=\"01918\" class=\"\">myrtles</st>, and <st data-num=\"08081\" class=\"\">olive</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">trees</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">grow</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"01265\" class=\"\">evergreens</st>, <st data-num=\"08410\" class=\"\">firs</st>, and <st data-num=\"08391\" class=\"\">cypresses</st> <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">grow</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st> in the <st data-num=\"06160\" class=\"\">arid rift valley</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will do this <st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">so</st><n id=\"1\" /> people<n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">observe</st> and <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">recognize</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">so they will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">pay attention</st> and <st data-num=\"07919 03162\">understand</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">power</st><n id=\"3\" /> has <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">accomplished</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and that the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">brought</st> it <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">into being</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"07126\" class=\"\">Present</st> your <st data-num=\"07379\" class=\"\">argument</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">Produce</st> your <st data-num=\"06110\" class=\"\">evidence</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cLet them <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">produce evidence</st>! Let them <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">tell</st> us <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> will <st data-num=\"07136\" class=\"\">happen</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Tell us <st data-num=\"04100 02007\">about</st> your <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">earlier predictive oracles</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so we may <st data-num=\"07760 03820\">examine</st> them<n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">see</st> <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">how</st> they were <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">fulfilled</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0176\" class=\"\">Or</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">decree</st> for us some <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">future events</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">Predict</st> how <st data-num=\"0857\" class=\"\">future events</st> will <st data-num=\"0268\" class=\"\">turn out</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so we might <st data-num=\"03045 03588\">know</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Yes</st>, <st data-num=\"03190 07489\">do</st> something <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">good</st> or something <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">bad</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">so we might <st data-num=\"08159 03372\">be</st> frightened and <st data-num=\"03372 03162\">in awe</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nothing</st>, and your <st data-num=\"06467\" class=\"\">accomplishments</st> are <st data-num=\"0659\" class=\"\">nonexistent</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the one who <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chooses</st> to worship you is <st data-num=\"08441\" class=\"\">disgusting</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">stirred up</st> one out of the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st><n id=\"1\" /> and he <st data-num=\"0857\" class=\"\">advances</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">one from the <st data-num=\"04217 08121\">eastern horizon</st> who <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">prays</st> in my <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"0947\">steps on</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05461\" class=\"\">rulers</st> <st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">as if</st> they were <st data-num=\"02563\" class=\"\">clay</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">like</st> a <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter</st> <st data-num=\"07429\" class=\"\">treading</st> the <st data-num=\"02916\" class=\"\">clay</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">decreed</st> this from the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">beginning</st>, so we could <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Who announced it<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">ahead of time</st>, so we could <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018He\u2019s <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">correct</st>\u2019?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">none</st> of them <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">decreed</st> it.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">none</st> of them <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">announced</st> it.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> you <st data-num=\"0561\" class=\"\">say anything</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> decreed to <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">here\u2019s</st> what will happen!\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">sent</st> a <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">herald</st> to <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">look</st>, but <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is no</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">among <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">them</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is no</st> one who <st data-num=\"03289\" class=\"\">serves as an adviser</st><p class=\"poetry\">that I might <st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">ask questions</st> and <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">receive</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">answers</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them <st data-num=\"0369\">are nothing</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">accomplishments</st> are <st data-num=\"0657\" class=\"\">nonexistent</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"05262\" class=\"\">metal images</st> <st data-num=\"07307 08414\">lack any real substance</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  }
